          "reviewBody": "I came Here 20 August 2023 that day was My CTET Exam so I spent whole day here. I can say this School's Rules regulations are Good nd I met Gaurd and Teachers they are too Good in My room were 2 Teachers Ma'am was too Good nd her nature was so Sweet nd Sir was also Good they are cool and Calm nd helping person 😎👍 So I can say this school was Good for me 😊But in the out of School place was not clean nd near by no Shops but U can take e-rickshaw and go Haldiram there u can get for eating 😊I Shared My experience that is  💯 percents Truth 👍😊",
