            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "SSN is a beautiful school. The teachers are absolutely amazing, inspirational and hardworking. I was a student here since 6th grade to 10th, and my experience has been nothing but positive. The ambience is very friendly and welcoming. Due independence is also given to children so that they are able to feels sense of responsibility and learn important life lessons. I'll always love this place. Management and infrastructure is top tier. The school gives equal importance to academics and extracurriculars, and furthermore teachers are very understanding and helpful. I met some of the best people in my life, here. The students are very hardworking too, and there's a sense of belonging and family here, that i know I'm not going to be getting anywhere else now.  129% recommend. ",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
