          "reviewBody": "Please don't send your children in this School.. The principal and the teachers are just not professional at all, focus only on rote learning, also, the teachers & principal don't have any civic sense to talk..\n\nDon't even feel like giving one star given an option. Pathetic School, worst staff ever, No standard of education.. The teachers are not competent enough to teach children based on New Education Policy but they are competent enough to harrass parents & their Children and take out their personal vengeance on parents and children and support favoritism.\n\nForget about standard of education, the way they work/ behave can make you mentally & emotionally  harrassed and depressed..",
