          "reviewBody": "Somerville School is a highly-regarded institution in Noida, known for its commitment to providing a well-rounded and high-quality education to its students. The school boasts a dedicated and experienced faculty, and offers a wide range of academic programs that are designed to challenge and inspire students. The school's state-of-the-art facilities and modern infrastructure provide an ideal learning environment, with the school offering a range of sports and extracurricular activities to the students. The school's emphasis on discipline, hard work, and character-building is evident in the students and the school has a strong reputation for producing well-rounded and successful graduates. The school's focus on international education and cultural exchange provides students a unique opportunity to broaden their perspective. Overall, Somerville School is an excellent choice for parents who are looking for a high-quality education for their children.",
